
As per the requirement, Restcontroller (ProductServiceController) component is created 
which will interact with service layer(productService) 

this service class will use repository classes to communicate with mysql db.

spring data jpa is used for implementing dao layer.

also written unit test cases as mentioned in assignment doc.


List of classes created as part of the assignment

	ProductServiceController.java
	ProductService.java
	ProductDaoRepository.java
	ProductPriceRepository.java
	Product.java
	productDTO.java
	productPrice.java
	ExceptionMessage.java
	ProductNotFoundException.java
	CustomizedResponseEntityExceptonHandler.java
	
	
	ProductDAORepositoryTest - to verify read and write operations to database tables
	ProductServiceTest - written unit test cases for service methods.
	
	